{"tid":1748552,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"投票結束後會即時點票 大家一定要到場監察","createTime":"2019-11-23T17:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T14:48:34.000Z","uid":131696,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"72c49ac3e4f28b240331460915eddf919283185e","tid":1748552,"uid":131696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:23:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/18/P2019111800637.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F18%2FP2019111800637.htm&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=49356bd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/18/P2019111800637.htm</a><br />\n投票時間由<span style=\"color: red;\">上午七時三十分至晚上十時三十分</span>。<br />\n<br />\n投票結束後，大部分一般投票站會轉為點票站，即場點算選票。投票站改裝為點票站後會對外開放，<span style=\"color: red;\">公眾人士可在點票站的指定範圍內觀看點票過程</span>。"},{"pid":"0a488538364016871239ad00a326a0c7fd2cea77","tid":1748552,"uid":314531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"佢老味唔好種票"},{"pid":"ec82c3ea907b451ef2101a42e7d278039527c1a9","tid":1748552,"uid":131696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:33:22.000Z","msg":"聽日再推"},{"pid":"8ad269d7e203a3b8956550f2c5c3a2cd9a591e62","tid":1748552,"uid":68111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上年都有去 一定要去"},{"pid":"b72ed3427dd1675dde2e2b2c1624f3a7716fcc19","tid":1748552,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezEboS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezEboS</a>"},{"pid":"b5adb2e6fd85311d32d42136f0e51